i (TV series)|Taxi]]'' || Roger Chapman || Episode: \"[[List of Taxi episodes#ep21|Hollywood Calling]]\"\n|-\n|1984 || ''[[The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson]]'' || Himself || Guest\n|-\n|1984 || ''[[Domestic Life (TV series)|Domestic Life]]'' || Martin Crane ||\n|-\n|1985 ||data-sort-value=\"History of White People in America, The\"| ''[[The History of White People in America]]'' || Himself ||\n|-\n|1985 || ''[[Lots of Luck]]'' || Frank Maris || [[Television film]]\n|-\n|1990 ||data-sort-value=\"Golden Girls, The\"| ''[[The Golden Girls]]'' || Jimmy || Episode: \"[[The Golden Girls (season 6)#ep132|Snap Out of It]]\"\n|-\n|1991 || ''[[Get a Life (TV series)|Get a Life]]'' || Sandy Connors ||\n|-\n|1991\u20131997 || ''[[Roseanne]]'' || Leon Carp || 46 episodes\n|-\n|1992\u20131993 ||data-sort-value=\"Larry Sanders Show, The\"| ''[[The Larry Sanders Show]]'' || Himself ||\n|-\n|1993 || ''[[Family Dog (TV series)|Family Dog]]'' || Skip Binsford (voice) ||\n|-\n|1995 || ''[[Lois & Clark: The New Adventures of Superman]]'' || Marlin Pfinch-Lupus || Episode: \"Whine, Whine, Whine\"\n|-\n|1997 || ''[[Over the Top (TV series)|Over the Top]]'' || Brookes Jenson || Episode: \"The Review\"\n|-\n|1997\u20132000 || ''[[Sabrina the Teenage Witch (1996 TV series)|Sabrina the Teenage Witch]]'' || Willard Kraft || 73 episodes\n|-\n|1998 || ''[[The Simpsons]]'' || Seth (voice) || Episode: \"[[D'oh-in' in the Wind]]\"\n|-\n|2000 || ''[[Family Guy]]'' || Mr. Harris (voice) || Episode: \"[[If I'm Dyin', I'm Lyin']]\"\n|-\n|2000 || ''[[Just Shoot Me!]]'' || Stan || Episode: \"Slamming Jack\"\n|-\n|2001\u20132002 ||data-sort-value=\"Ellen Show, The\"| ''[[The Ellen Show]]'' || Ed Munn || 18 episodes\n|-\n|2001 || ''[[That '70s Show]]'' || Voice of Donna's journal || Episode: \"[[That '70s Show (season 3)#ep73|Eric's Drunken Tattoo]]\n|-\n|2002 || ''[[Dexter's Laboratory]]'' || M.A.R. 10 (voice) || Episode: \"[[List of Dexter's Laboratory episodes#ep58b|Lab on the Run]]\"\n|-\n|2002 